frames.caption: A majestic ship sails through a narrow icy river, surrounded by snow-laden trees and mountains. The vibrant aurora borealis illuminates the night sky, casting colorful reflections on the water. The scene is serene and magical, with the ship's warm lights contrasting against the cool blues of the landscape.
frames.description: The scene depicts a large ship navigating through a frozen river in a mountainous, snow-covered landscape. The aurora borealis lights up the night sky, creating a mystical atmosphere.
